---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Warsaw Preview II — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Warsaw Preview II</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Jazdów, Warsaw | 2020</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Open-air contemporary art showcase, creating a pleasant picnic atmosphere accompanied by the sounds of DJs from Radio Kapitał. The 2020 edition focused on small sculptural forms, with participating artists reinterpreting the broader concept of sculpture within the park setting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Curators:</strong> Kamil Pierwszy, Eryka Anioł, Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Justyna Smoleł, Konrad Ciszkowski, Oleg Kaska, Paulina Joda, Kuba Mozolewski, Jagoda Dobecka</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/warsaw-preview/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/warsaw-preview/2.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
